case.name: Blessing!
case.description: Aqua will use the luck buffing spell "Blessing" on herself after losing a few times. This is by most accounts, cheating, or at least seen as a dirty tactic.

notes.note: I believe Aqua is actually too lazy to go through with this, so that could potentially come up if Noire mentions the work it takes to be an idol.

Aqua says this even if Aqua KH is present on purpose, if Noire wants to point out that there's another Aqua present with them, feel free to, I can already picture Aqua's response, and potentially it could turn into a three-way target if Nord was down for it.

My intent with this line is to have Noire talk about her fellow goddesses, like Neptune, Blanc, Vert, and so on. I assume she'll focus on Neptune if she's also in the table with them. If you want to ask Aqua about what gods she knows of with Noire, you can, but keep in mind that I'll only have her mention the goddess Eris, as the other deities that appear in Konosuba are ones this Aqua wouldn't know about yet.
Yes, Aqua cycled things back around just to praise herself. I also gave the markers different values in case you want to target her using the word goddess specifically
Yes this is an exceedingly dumb question
Aqua DOES know about the "real world" so it wouldn't be unreasonable to believe she knows about Uno, however I think it's funny if she doesn't know/forgot
I'm thinking I might have Aqua insist that he joins her party depending on how he answers. But you can have him answer however you wish! (^-^)b

Aqua is rambling about herself and her own annoyances more than properly answering, and also just name drops Eris. It's perfectly reasonable if Mia were to not know who Eris is, or even that she's a goddess as well. But you can respond any way you wish! (^-^)b
She does not get it at all
I'm thinking that Aqua might think about how she wants to get one for herself if Mia explains more about the Djinn
It's worth noting that Perona *already* explained her ability when she talked about the Hollow Hollow Fruit, Aqua was just too busy looking at the ghost to pay attention.
Just FYI, these lines have two different markers
